 ğŸ§© 4. Problem Statement  

> **Problem Statement:**  
> Electric Vehicle users often experience uncertainty about their driving range due to variations in temperature, terrain, driving behavior, and battery health.  
>  
> This project aims to research and develop a framework that can **forecast the real-world range of EVs** by analyzing various operational and environmental parameters â€” thereby reducing range anxiety and improving the overall EV experience.

